---
import { Paragraph } from "../components/Paragraph/Paragraph";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Swarnim Walavalkar — questions" description="questions">
  <main class="prose">
    <h1 class="text-2xl">Big Questions</h1>

    <Paragraph>
      Questions and problems I've been curious about and would like to contribute
      towards in my lifetime.
    </Paragraph>

    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">
      Inspired by <a
        class="underline decoration-neutral-700 underline-offset-3 transition-colors duration-200 hover:decoration-neutral-400"
        href="https://patrickcollison.com/questions"
        target="_blank">Patrick Collison's Questions</a>
    </p>

    <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 list-none pl-0">
      <li class="border-l-2 border-neutral-800 pl-4 text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-200">Can we cure autoimmune disorders?</li>
      <li class="border-l-2 border-neutral-800 pl-4 text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-200">Can we build Singularity?</li>
      <li class="border-l-2 border-neutral-800 pl-4 text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-200">
        Can we longitudinally study humans so we can predict when they will fall
        ill?
      </li>
      <li class="border-l-2 border-neutral-800 pl-4 text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-200">Can we detect disease through continuous non-invasive monitoring?</li>
      <li class="border-l-2 border-neutral-800 pl-4 text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-200">Is there a way to reverse or mitigate climate change?</li>
      <li class="border-l-2 border-neutral-800 pl-4 text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-200">Can we create a livable habitat on another planet?</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
